for i in boss[''].index:
    try:
        boss[''][i]=boss[''][i].split('')[0]
    except:
        pass
for i in boss[''].index:
    if 'K' in boss[''][i]:
        min=boss[''][i].replace('K','').split('-')[0]
        max=boss[''][i].replace('K','').split('-')[1]
        boss[''][i]=((int(min)*1000)+(int(max)*1000))/2
    elif '/' in boss[''][i]:
        try:
            min=boss[''][i].replace('/','').split('-')[0]
            max=boss[''][i].replace('/','').split('-')[1]
            boss[''][i]=((int(min)+int(max))/2)*30
        except:
            max=boss[''][i].replace('/','')
            boss[''][i]=float(max)*30
    elif '/' in boss[''][i]:
        min=boss[''][i].replace('/','').split('-')[0]
        max=boss[''][i].replace('/','').split('-')[1]
        boss[''][i]=(((int(min)*8)+(int(max)*8))/2)*30
    elif '/' in boss[''][i]:
        min=boss[''][i].replace('/','').split('-')[0]
        max=boss[''][i].replace('/','').split('-')[1]
        boss[''][i]=(int(min)+int(max))/2

word_count = {}
for word in words:
    if word not in word_count:
        word_count[word] = 1
    else:
        word_count[word] += 1
